# SmartCart -- Customer Segmentation Project
Hi
This is my SmartCart Customer Segmentation project.
In this project, I used Machine Learning clustering techniques
to group customers based on income, age, and spending behaviour.-------------------------------------------------------------------
About the Project
The main goal of this project is to analyze customer data
and identify different types of customers using ML techniques.
Things I practiced in this project:- Data cleaning- Handling missing values- Removing outliers- Feature scaling- Customer clustering- Data visualization-------------------------------------------------------------------
Technologies Used- Python- NumPy- Pandas- Matplotlib- Seaborn- Scikit-learn- Jupyter Notebook-------------------------------------------------------------------
Project Workflow
1. Import required libraries
2. Load the dataset
3. Handle missing values
4. Remove outliers
5. Encode categorical data
6. Scale the features using StandardScaler
7. Apply clustering algorithms
8. Analyze the clusters-------------------------------------------------------------------
Clustering Methods Used- K-Means Clustering- Agglomerative Clustering- Elbow Method- Silhouette Score-------------------------------------------------------------------
How to Run the Project
1. Clone the repository
2. Open the notebook in Jupyter Notebook
3. Run all cells step by step-------------------------------------------------------------------
Final Note
This project is part of my Machine Learning learning journey.
I am continuously learning and improving my skills.

